	CDN buckets:

		- wac.41aa.edgecastcdn.net/??41AA/

			- cdn


	Nonfunctional domains:

		- sitepoint.com subdomains:

			- cdn		(404; mismatched, CN: gp1.wac.edgecastcdn.net)
			- downtime *
			- products *
			- tools *

		- (www.)sitepointstatic.com ³
		- 1.sitepointstatic.com *

	* Refused
	³ Shows beyonce


	Problematic domains:

		- sitepoint.com subdomains:

			- beyonce ¹
			- community *
			- i2 ³
			- reference *
			- xmas *

	¹ Self-signed
	* Mismatched
	³ Shows beyonce


